OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1784380679
OL,3,CVickrum Digwa's mother jailed for
OL,4,Cremoving knife from scene of murder
OL,6,FThe mother of Vickrum Digwa has been
OL,7,Fjailed for removing the knife from the
OL,8,Fscene of Henry Nowak's murder in
OL,9,FSouthampton.
OL,11,FDigwa, 23, was jailed for life for the
OL,12,Fmurder of 18-year-old university
OL,13,Fstudent Henry Nowak who he stabbed in
OL,14,FDecember last year. He had falsely
OL,15,Fclaimed Mr Nowak had racially abused
OL,16,Fhim.
OL,18,FHe was sentenced to a minimum of 21
OL,19,Fyears behind bars in June.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/12
