PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1784380679
OL,3,CVickrum Digwa's mother jailed for
OL,4,Cremoving knife from scene of murder
OL,6,FHis mother, Kiran Kaur, 53, of St
OL,7,FDenys Road, Southampton, was found
OL,8,Fguilty of assisting an offender on the
OL,9,Fnight of the murder on December 3 2025
OL,10,Fby taking the weapon back to the
OL,11,Fnearby family home.
OL,13,FShe appeared at Southampton Crown
OL,14,FCourt on Friday 17 July where she was
OL,15,Fjailed for three years.
OL,17,FSentencing Kaur, Judge William Mousley
OL,18,FKC said: "A responsible parent would
OL,19,Fhave challenged their son over their
OL,20,Factions and encourage them to do the
OL,21,Fright thing.
OL,26,@zD@JOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1784380679
OL,3,CVickrum Digwa's mother jailed for
OL,4,Cremoving knife from scene of murder
OL,6,F"Instead you took the knife home and
OL,7,Fput it with a larger collection of
OL,8,Fceremonial and other weapons in your
OL,9,Fson's bedroom.
OL,11,F"That would have helped to conceal
OL,12,Fwhat it had been used for.
OL,14,F"This is because you wanted him to
OL,15,Favoid being caught."
OL,17,FThe judge said her actions at Belmont
OL,18,FRoad before and after taking the
OL,19,Fdagger away "added to your son's
OL,20,Fpretence that he had done nothing
OL,21,Fwrong and that he was the victim".
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUvD@AOUwD@TO]{D@MOU}D@aO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1784380679
OL,3,CVickrum Digwa's mother jailed for
OL,4,Cremoving knife from scene of murder
OL,6,FThe court heard the knife was
OL,7,Frecovered after examination of CCTV,
OL,8,Fand determined by the police to be the
OL,9,Fmurder weapon about a week after Mr
OL,10,FNowak was killed.
OL,12,FProsecutor Nicholas Lobbenberg KC had
OL,13,Ftold the court her role was "crucial"
OL,14,Fin removing the murder weapon at a
OL,15,Ftime the police were coming to the
OL,16,Fscene.
OL,26,@uD@]OUuD@eO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1784380679
OL,3,CVickrum Digwa's mother jailed for
OL,4,Cremoving knife from scene of murder
OL,6,FHe said: "The absence of weapon at the
OL,7,Fscene caused by her actions hampered
OL,8,Fthe police attending who were, as your
OL,9,FHonour will recall, were confronted
OL,10,Fwith a wall of lies.
OL,12,F"She chose not to disclose what she
OL,13,Fhad done.
OL,15,F"Absence of that weapon led to Henry
OL,16,Fdying terrified, alone and
OL,17,Fdisbelieved, her actions contributed
OL,18,Fto this."
OL,26,@nD@JOUtD@AOUwD@AOUzD@IO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1784380679
OL,3,CVickrum Digwa's mother jailed for
OL,4,Cremoving knife from scene of murder
OL,6,FBarrister Mark Watson, defending Kaur,
OL,7,Fsaid at the time of the incident Kaur
OL,8,Fonly became involved after receiving a
OL,9,Fphone call that her son had been
OL,10,Fattacked, as she was getting ready for
OL,11,Fbed.
OL,13,FHe said the mother was "equally
OL,14,Fmisled" as Digwa lied to those around
OL,15,Fhim about what happened.
OL,17,FHe said what she did was a
OL,18,F"spontaneous" act, not a calculated
OL,19,Fplan, adding: "The weapon was not
OL,20,Fdestroyed, it was not cleaned, it was
OL,21,Fnot broken up and hidden."
OL,26,@uD@XOUvD@GO]zD@AOUzD@MO]{D@OOU}D@ZO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1784380679
OL,3,CVickrum Digwa's mother jailed for
OL,4,Cremoving knife from scene of murder
OL,6,FThe knife was still within its sheath,
OL,7,Fhe added.
OL,9,F"Offending arose during a moment of
OL,10,Fpanic and human frailty, the court may
OL,11,Fthink," he said.
OL,13,FHe said the mother-of-five was a
OL,14,Fpillar of her family and community and
OL,15,Fshowed positive good character before
OL,16,Fthe incident, including through
OL,17,Fvolunteer work, as he urged the judge
OL,18,Fto hand down a suspended sentence.
OL,26,@qD@AOUsD@GO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1784380679
OL,3,CVickrum Digwa's mother jailed for
OL,4,Cremoving knife from scene of murder
OL,6,FBut the judge said when Digwa told her
OL,7,Fto take the murder weapon, sheath and
OL,8,Fbelt away, "by then you knew or
OL,9,Fbelieved that he had stabbed and
OL,10,Finjured Henry".
OL,12,F"Even if you might have believed that
OL,13,Fyour son had been racially abused and
OL,14,Fassaulted, you knew there could be no
OL,15,Fjustification for him to have stabbed
OL,16,FHenry. Your son had no significant
OL,17,Finjury," he said.
OL,26,@pD@LOUrD@NO]tD@AOUyD@HO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1784380679
OL,3,CVickrum Digwa's mother jailed for
OL,4,Cremoving knife from scene of murder
OL,6,FThe judge acknowledged that Kaur is
OL,7,Funlikely to reoffend and her actions
OL,8,Fwere "mistakenly, to protect your son
OL,9,Frather than for any personal gain".
OL,11,FBut Judge Mousley added: "However, the
OL,12,Fseriousness of your offending,
OL,13,Frequires you to be punished and others
OL,14,Fwho might find themselves in a similar
OL,15,Fsituation to be deterred from doing as
OL,16,Fyou did."
OL,18,FIn his remarks, the judge set out the
OL,19,F"devastating and lifelong impact" of
OL,20,FMr Nowak's death on his family.
OL,26,@pD@FOUqD@bO]sD@ZOUxD@IO]{D@AOU{D@aO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1784380679
OL,3,CVickrum Digwa's mother jailed for
OL,4,Cremoving knife from scene of murder
OL,6,FHe described the first year university
OL,7,Fstudent as a "much-loved, kind, hard-
OL,8,Fworking and ambitious young man
OL,9,Fdevoted to his family and with a
OL,10,Fbright future".
OL,12,FKaur has spent more than seven months
OL,13,Fin custody since her arrest.
OL,15,FMembers of her family also attended
OL,16,Fthe court hearing, supporting her from
OL,17,Fthe public gallery.
OL,26,@oD@NOUrD@NO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1784380679
OL,3,CVickrum Digwa's mother jailed for
OL,4,Cremoving knife from scene of murder
OL,6,FKelly Newman, of the Crown Prosecution
OL,7,FService, said: "Henry Nowak was just
OL,8,F18 years old when he was murdered by
OL,9,FVickrum Digwa and our thoughts remain
OL,10,Fwith Henry's family and loved ones,
OL,11,Fwho have endured unimaginable loss.
OL,13,F"Digwa lied to police about Henry
OL,14,Fafter carrying out the senseless act
OL,15,Fof violence and in the immediate
OL,16,Faftermath, Kiran Kaur chose to help
OL,17,Fher son by removing the murder weapon
OL,18,Fin a deliberate attempt to obstruct
OL,19,Fthe investigation and hide crucial
OL,20,Fevidence.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1784380679
OL,3,CVickrum Digwa's mother jailed for
OL,4,Cremoving knife from scene of murder
OL,6,F"Those who seek to help murderers
OL,7,Fevade justice should be in no doubt
OL,8,Fthat they too will be held accountable
OL,9,Ffor their actions."
OL,26,@qD@SO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/12
